---
title: Black Bean and Farro Salad with Apples and Cilantro Vinaigrette
description: Black beans and farro team up beautifully in this ultra-hearty grain salad. The duo pairs unexpectedly well with crunchy Granny Smith apple and creamy avocado. A bright cilantro and shallot vinaigrette ties the whole dish together.
